3ï¸âƒ£ X-XSS-Protection (Prevents XSS in Older Browsers)
Purpose: Enables built-in browser XSS filters (now deprecated).
Directives:
0 â†’ Disables protection.
1 â†’ Enables XSS filtering.
1; mode=block â†’ Blocks the page if an attack is detected.
